  </svg>
</div>
```

### CSS Styling

**Site Header (.site-header):**
```css
.site-header {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 18px 22px 0;
  min-height: 46px;
}
```

**Hamburger Button (.hamburger):**
```css
.hamburger {
  background: none;
  border: none;
  padding: 8px 0;
  cursor: pointer;
  justify-self: start;
}
.hamburger svg {
  display: block;
}
```

**Logo Link (.logo-link):**
```css
.logo-link {
  line-height: 0;
}
.logo-link img {
  width: 108px;
  height: 27px;
  display: block;
}
```

**Cart Button (.cart-btn):**
```css
.cart-btn {
  background: none;
  border: none;
  padding: 6px 0;
  cursor: pointer;
  justify-self: end;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
}
.cart-btn svg {
  display: block;
}
```

**Search Bar (.search-bar):**
```css
.search-bar {
  margin: 17px 17px 0 19px;
  height: 49px;
  background: #F4F4F4;
  border-radius: 8px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 0 15px 0 22px;
  gap: 8px;
}
```

**Search Input:**
```css
.search-bar input {
  flex: 1;
  min-width: 0;
  border: none;
  background: transparent;
  font: 300 14px/1 'Bagoss Extended', sans-serif;
  color: #000;
  outline: none;
  letter-spacing: 0.01em;
}

.search-bar input::placeholder {
  color: #000;
  opacity: 1;
}
```

**Search Icon (SVG):**
```css
.search-bar svg {
  flex-shrink: 0;
  width: 15px;
  height: 15px;
}
```

### Key Layout Details

- **Header layout:** 3-column grid (hamburger | logo | cart) with flexible outer columns and fixed center
- **Header height:** Minimum 46px with 18px top padding
- **Search bar dimensions:** 49px height with 17px top margin and 8px gap between input and icon
- **Search bar background:** Light gray (#F4F4F4) with 8px border radius
- **Font:** Bagoss Extended family, 300 weight, 14px size for input text
- **Search placeholder:** Swedish "Søk etter produkter" (hunt) or "Sök efter produkter" (dogs/outdoor variants)

